title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Sim Update 12 - new build available
description:
In this video we will have a look at what has been fixed in the new build which has just been made available for Sim Update 12. In this build a few fixes have been implemented but it is a relatively small list compared to the previous build.

The full list of fixes can be found via the link below:
https://forums.flightsimulator.com/t/beta-update-1-31-21-0-march-9th-2023/580404
